    <item>
      <title>萨格称肯尼亚准备捍卫当前先令汇率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kenya-prepared-to-defend-shilling-at-current-levels-thugge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚央行行长卡马乌·图格 (Kamau Thugge) 表示，今年先令汇率在创下世界最高纪录后，目前处于适当水平，政策制定者准备动用创纪录的外汇储备来捍卫先令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kenya-prepared-to-defend-shilling-at-current-levels-thugge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔毒枭被捕为诺沃亚在危机中助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瓜亚基尔电视台袭击案两名嫌疑人在西班牙被捕，此次袭击事件引起了全球关注，并引发了厄瓜多尔打击黑帮的战争，这给厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚在严重的电力危机中提供了急需的鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/arrest-of-top-ecuador-drug-lords-hands-noboa-much-needed-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 19:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
